# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:76
translate korean e08s02_bc4608e2:

    # mc "What's the haul looking like?"
    mc "양은 어때?"

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:80
translate korean e08s02_86515e76:

    # arj "Looking pretty good. There's a few cracked ones, and a few wet ones, but all in all, at least a dozen."
    arj "꽤 괜찮아 보여. 깨진 거 몇 개, 젖은 것도 몇 개, 그래서 도합 열두 개는 되지."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:83
translate korean e08s02_742b44c0:

    # mc "A dozen? Wow, that's great."
    mc "열두 개? 와아, 대단한데."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:86
translate korean e08s02_d57241b9:

    # arj "Wish I can give the moms a treat. Like how we give Remy raw meat every once in a while."
    arj "암탉들한텐 상으로 먹을 거라도 주면 좋을 거 같은데. 레미한테는 가끔 생고기를 주잖아."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:89
translate korean e08s02_fce6bb30:

    # mc "I'm glad chickens only eat feed. I don't want meat-eating chickens."
    mc "닭들이 사료만 먹어서 다행이지. 나는 고기 먹는 닭은 싫거든."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:90
translate korean e08s02_cf51afe0:

    # mc "I wouldn't be able to sleep at night, because I'd be afraid of them coming in the house and eating me."
    mc "그러면 날 잡아먹을까 봐 두려워서 밤에는 잠도 못 잘 거라고."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:92
translate korean e08s02_0d6f54b6:

    # arj "Yeah, you already have one person eating you, and that's enough."
    arj "그래, 밤에 널 먹는 사람은 따로 있으니, 그걸로 충분하지."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:94
translate korean e08s02_3bafe7f5:

    # mc "Get your mind out of the gutter!"
    mc "지저분한 이야기는 꺼내지도 마!"

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:97
translate korean e08s02_97b2efbc:

    # arj "I can't. Especially not after that last session."
    arj "못하겠는데. 우리가 마지막에 했던 짓을 생각하면 더욱."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:105
translate korean e08s02_d9e41a2d:

    # mc "You're incorrigible."
    mc "정말 구제불능이라니까."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:107
translate korean e08s02_10b4fd90:

    # arj "I mean it, that was really good. I haven't felt this good in a while."
    arj "진심으로 한 말이야. 정말 끝내 줬으니까. 오랜만에 정말 기분 좋았어."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:108
translate korean e08s02_fc02a2ca:

    # mc "What's changed?"
    mc "뭐가 달라진 거지?"

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:109
translate korean e08s02_bc7d21b5:

    # arj "I'm not sure."
    arj "잘 모르겠는데."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:113
translate korean e08s02_65260b06:

    # mc "Settle down, girl! The cows are already in here."
    mc "진정해, 욘석아! 소들은 이미 안에 들어왔어."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:115
translate korean e08s02_c419e287:

    # arj "I think she's barking at something else."
    arj "다른 걸 보고 짖는 거 같아."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:119
translate korean e08s02_11455b53:

    # mc "What?"
    mc "뭘 보고?"

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:121
translate korean e08s02_7f544e08:

    # arj "Probably at that storm approaching."
    arj "아마 곧 온다는 폭풍 때문에 짖는 거겠지."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:123
translate korean e08s02_a39b627f:

    # mc "Right, then."
    mc "그래, 그렇겠다."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:124
translate korean e08s02_d317b47f:

    # mc "Let's finish up cleaning the barn, and get all the animals inside, so we can start boarding up the windows."
    mc "헛간 청소 마무리하고, 가축들은 다 안으로 들여오자. 그래야 창문 막을 준비를 하지."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:125
translate korean e08s02_8e1b3ec2:

    # mc "Do we know when it's going to hit?"
    mc "폭풍이 언제 오는 건지 알아?"

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:128
translate korean e08s02_45b299a7:

    # arj "Tomorrow, I think."
    arj "내일인 거 같아."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:131
translate korean e08s02_3db30863:

    # mc "Seriously? That quick?"
    mc "진짜로? 그렇게 빨리?"

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:132
translate korean e08s02_676bbd3b:

    # mc "That's one downside of living out here. In the city, I had never seen a tornado or a hurricane."
    mc "시골에 사는 단점이 이거라니까. 도시에서는 평생 토네이도나 허리케인은 본 적도 없는데."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:134
translate korean e08s02_4d52a5fd:

    # arj "I just hope it's not too bad."
    arj "큰 문제없이 넘어가야 할 텐데."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:137
translate korean e08s02_060e40ef:

    # mc "I should call the neighbors and let them know."
    mc "이웃들한테 전화해서 알려 줘야겠다."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:140
translate korean e08s02_b67cc297:

    # arj "Well, I think they do know, that's why they came over. They're preparing for the storm too."
    arj "글쎄, 이미 다들 알고 있지 않을까? 우리 집에 들린 이유도 폭풍 때문일 거야. 다들 대비하고 있겠지."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:142
translate korean e08s02_b8de06d3:

    # mc "Oh."
    mc "아."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:143
translate korean e08s02_a7c62671:

    # arj "Yeah."
    arj "그래."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:146
translate korean e08s02_f3ad781a:

    # mc "Then what was that thing about the game? And cheese curds?"
    mc "그럼 그 장난은 다 뭐였던 거야? 생치즈는 뭐고?"

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:149
translate korean e08s02_269f28f6:

    # arj "I assume they don't think it'd be that bad."
    arj "그렇게 심각하진 않을 거라고 보는 거 아닐까."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:153
translate korean e08s02_0b2d0da4:

    # mc "Well, they would know, they've been here a lot longer than we have."
    mc "흠, 이웃들이 우리보다 여기 오래 살았으니까. 더 잘알겠지."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:154
translate korean e08s02_a5713ad3:

    # mc "Let's hope they're right."
    mc "진짜로 심각하지 않아야 하는데."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:155
translate korean e08s02_07f329cc:

    # mc "I really need to check the weather forecast every now and again."
    mc "지금부터라도 일기 예보를 계속 확인해야겠어."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:157
translate korean e08s02_5b1957aa:

    # arj "When's the last time you used your phone?"
    arj "너 휴대폰은 쓰긴 하니?"

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:160
translate korean e08s02_52f197e7:

    # mc "Honestly, not that much."
    mc "아니, 거의 안 쓰지."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:161
translate korean e08s02_62a957a5:

    # mc "I get texts from Stacy every now and again."
    mc "그래도 종종 스테이시한테 오는 문자는 봐."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:164
translate korean e08s02_9e365426:

    # arj "Really? What's she up to now?"
    arj "그래? 스테이시는 요즘 뭐해?"

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:167
translate korean e08s02_063d1a03:

    # mc "She's on vacation in Japan. She sent me some photos of her on Fuji-san."
    mc "일본에서 휴가 중이라고 하더라. 후지산에서 찍은 사진도 보내 줬어."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:168
translate korean e08s02_a1326573:

    # mc "Apparently it's quite dirty there."
    mc "꽤 지저분하더라."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:169
translate korean e08s02_38b22955:

    # mc "But other than that, not much. I mean, I get it. Everyone's pretty busy and all. It is a bit isolating though, isn't it?"
    mc "다른 사람들한테는 연락의 거의 없어. 다들 바쁘니가 이해는 되는데, 그래도 좀 고립된 느낌이 든다니까. 그치?"

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:170
translate korean e08s02_b89309aa:

    # mc "Being away from other people."
    mc "다른 사람들과 떨어져 사니까 말이야."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:173
translate korean e08s02_4da58625:

    # arj "Well, people are always a phone call away. Or a walk. Not like we live in the desert."
    arj "글쎄, 전화 한 통이면 언제든지 사람들이랑 연락할 수 있잖아. 아니면, 직접 가 볼 수도 있고. 우리가 무슨 사막에 사는 것도 아니까."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:174
translate korean e08s02_cc07ae0a:

    # mc "I haven't really gotten a chance to talk to others now that I think about it."
    mc "생각해 보니까, 요즘은 다른 사람들이랑 이야기할 기회도 별도 없네."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:175
translate korean e08s02_8e788348:

    # arj "Shame there's no coffee shop or anything to talk to people around here. There is a library around here, though it's pretty empty most of the time."
    arj "이 주변에 커피숍 같은 곳이나 주변 사람들이랑 이야기할 만한 곳이 없다는 게 정말 아쉬워. 도서관이 있긴 하지만, 사람도 거의 없더라구."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:178
translate korean e08s02_aacbae05:

    # mc "I mean, that's not such a bad thing, right?"
    mc "그래도 그게 그렇게 나쁜 건 아니잖아?"

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:179
translate korean e08s02_9654c5dc:

    # arj "You mean silence?"
    arj "조용해서 좋으니까?"

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:180
translate korean e08s02_e334e13f:

    # mc "Something like that."
    mc "그런 거지."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:183
translate korean e08s02_57bec497:

    # arj "Silence is good, yeah."
    arj "그래, 조용한 건 좋지."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:184
translate korean e08s02_f4e85547:

    # arj "I find it better to talk to others too though."
    arj "그치만 난 다른 사람들이랑 이야기하는 것도 좋아하는걸."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:186
translate korean e08s02_10a3781b:

    # mc "That's one thing I liked about being in college. Just being in proximity with other people, you know? I could walk outside my room and find other people to talk to. And everyone always wanted something."
    mc "대학 다닐 땐 그게 좋았어. 근처에 언제나 사람들이 있다는 점 말이야. 방에서 나오기만 해도 이야기할 사람들이 있었고, 항상 뭔가를 이야기하고 싶어 했지."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:187
translate korean e08s02_1fe77c46:

    # mc "And now, it's pretty quiet."
    mc "그런데 지금은, 정말 조용해."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:193
translate korean e08s02_cd8a5d2c:

    # arj "You know, I was reading a biography of a band that I like, and in it, the author described how bands on average stay together for about seven to eight years."
    arj "그 말하니까 생각난다. 내가 좋아하는 밴드의 전기를 읽어 보니까, 거기서 밴드가 함께 하는 기간이 평규 7~8년 정도라는 거야."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:194
translate korean e08s02_57cd78d4:

    # arj "That coincides with the average time when a marriage falls apart."
    arj "그게 결혼이 유지되는 평균 햇수랑 딱 맞더라구."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:195
translate korean e08s02_5e4f424a:

    # arj "Isn't that a big shame?"
    arj "정말 아쉽지 않아?"

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:197
translate korean e08s02_a16db31d:

    # mc "It is."
    mc "그러게."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:200
translate korean e08s02_b3d48372:

    # arj "I mean being together for that long, just to grow to hate each other, I mean, that's a tragedy."
    arj "그렇게 오래 함께하다가 서로를 증오하게 된다는 건 정말 비극이지."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:201
translate korean e08s02_d13bf679:

    # arj "I don't want anything like that to happen to us, you know."
    arj "우리는 그렇게 되면 안 돼."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:203
translate korean e08s02_45de1ca3:

    # mc "Why would that happen?"
    mc "그런 일이 왜 생기겠어?"

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:206
translate korean e08s02_aecca327:

    # arj "I'm not saying it will."
    arj "그럴 거라고 하는 말은 아니야."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:207
translate korean e08s02_bab16cbb:

    # arj "I'm just wondering if we can beat the odds."
    arj "우리가 그런 위기를 견뎌낼 확률이 궁금한 거지."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:210
translate korean e08s02_40a9c3a8:

    # mc "Well, I'm happy now, and you're happy now, and isn't that what matters? We can worry about the future but it won't help anything."
    mc "글쎄, 난 지금 행복해. 너도 지금 행복하고. 중요한 건 그거잖아? 지금이 중요하지, 앞으로 어떻게 될지도 모른다고 걱정하는 건 의미없어."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:211
translate korean e08s02_9e3a8b68:

    # mc "We just have to worry about getting through this day."
    mc "우리는 오늘 하루를 잘 보내는 것만 걱정하면 돼."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:214
translate korean e08s02_ef858acc:

    # arj "You're right."
    arj "네 말이 맞아."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:215
translate korean e08s02_0214499b:

    # arj "I don't know what fell over me. I guess I'm feeling a little bit worried about the storm, and all. Sorry."
    arj "나도 왜 그런 걱정을 하는지 모르겠어. 폭풍이 온다는 것 때문에 별별 생각이 다 드나 봐. 미안."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:218
translate korean e08s02_de9794b7:

    # mc "Nothing to feel sorry for. Let's clean the nests and then start boarding up the barn, and then we'll take a nice, long bath together, how's that sound?"
    mc "미안해 하지 않아도 돼. 둥지 청소하고 헛간 문짝 막기나 하자구. 그다음엔 편안하고 길게 같이 목욕을 하는 거야, 좋지?"

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:220
translate korean e08s02_c7076d0b:

    # arj "That sounds good."
    arj "듣기만 해도 좋은걸."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:221
translate korean e08s02_aefbe0e6:

    # arj "But before that, I want to say something."
    arj "근데, 그 전에 할 말이 있어."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:223
translate korean e08s02_def0ad19:

    # mc "What is it?"
    mc "뭔데?"

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:226
translate korean e08s02_76edcfcf:

    # arj "Well, you know, I don't want this marriage to fall into a routine."
    arj "음, 있잖아. 난 우리 결혼이 쳇바퀴 도는 것처럼 변하는 건 원하지 않아."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:227
translate korean e08s02_23fbf480:

    # arj "And I don't want to lie to you either."
    arj "그리고 너한테 거짓말하고 싶지도 않고."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:228
translate korean e08s02_36d3de2d:

    # arj "There was something I wanted to do for a long time, but I haven't felt ready to say it."
    arj "오랫동안 너한테 하고 싶었던 게 있는데, 아직 말할 준비가 안 됐어."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:231
translate korean e08s02_5578bffd:

    # mc "You know you can tell me anything. Is there something wrong?"
    mc "나한텐 무슨 말이라도 해도 된다는 거 알잖아. 무슨 문제라도 있어?"

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:234
translate korean e08s02_1c596998:

    # arj "No, it's nothing serious like that."
    arj "아니, 심각한 건 아냐."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:235
translate korean e08s02_b7e29af4:

    # arj "But I don't want you to think lower of me."
    arj "그치만 네가 날 아랫것으로 보는 건 싫어."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:238
translate korean e08s02_5e0a4184:

    # mc "Lower of you?"
    mc "아랫것이라구?"

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:239
translate korean e08s02_a013e959:

    # mc "AmRose, you know how much I love you, right? You have nothing to be ashamed about, whatever you want to tell me, say it."
    mc "앰로즈, 내가 널 얼마나 사랑하는지 알잖아? 네가 주저할 만한 건 아무것도 없어. 하고 싶은 말이 있으면, 뭐든 해."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:242
translate korean e08s02_f7d709cd:

    # arj "Okay, well..."
    arj "알겠어, 음..."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:243
translate korean e08s02_f0966344:

    # arj "It's about our sex life."
    arj "우리 성생활에 관한 거야."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:245
translate korean e08s02_6651ab87:

    # mc "Alright."
    mc "그렇구나."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:252
translate korean e08s02_73686ede:

    # arj "I want to try something. Something new."
    arj "난 우리가 뭔가 해 보면 좋겠어. 뭔가 새로운 거."

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:254
translate korean e08s02_4e06e94c:

    # mc "Is it Frank? Ashley?"
    mc "프랭크 말하는 거야? 애슐리?"

# game/code/e08/e08s02.rpy:255
translate korean e08s02_e1715634:

    # arj "No, not really."
    arj "아니, 그런 게 아냐."

